msgid "The Journey of a Seed"
msgstr "Safari ya Mbegu"

msgid "One clear pipeline, from request to receipt."
msgstr "Njia moja wazi, kuanzia ombi hadi upokeaji."

msgid "Register"
msgstr "Jisajili"

msgid "A farmer registers themselves, or their Village Officer registers them."
msgstr "Mkulima hujisajili mwenyewe, au Afisa wake wa Kijiji humsajili."

msgid ""
"The farmer requests a seed type for the season, straight from their own "
"login."
msgstr "Mkulima huomba aina ya mbegu kwa msimu, moja kwa moja kutoka akaunti yake mwenyewe."

msgid "Their Extension Officer verifies the request before it moves forward."
msgstr "Afisa wake wa Ugani huthibitisha ombi kabla halijaendelea."

msgid "Receive"
msgstr "Pokea"

msgid ""
"The Village Officer fulfills it from real stock, and the farmer confirms "
