msgstr "Afisa wa Kijiji hutimiza kutoka hifadhi halisi, na mkulima huthibitisha kupokea."

msgid "See the Full Picture"
msgstr "Ona Mtazamo Kamili"

msgid "Built for Everyone in the Chain"
msgstr "Imejengwa kwa Kila Mtu Ndani ya Mnyororo"

msgid "One System, Every Role"
msgstr "Mfumo Mmoja, Kila Jukumu"

msgid ""
"Register, request seeds, track status, confirm receipt and give feedback - "
