msgstr "Jisajili, omba mbegu, fuatilia hali, thibitisha upokeaji na toa maoni - yote kutoka akaunti moja."

msgid "Extension Officers"
msgstr "Maafisa wa Ugani"

msgid ""
"Verify farmer requests, help farmers use the system, and resolve complaints "
"in their ward."
msgstr "Thibitisha maombi ya wakulima, saidia wakulima kutumia mfumo, na tatua malalamiko katika kata yao."

msgid "Village & Ward Officers"
msgstr "Maafisa wa Kijiji na Kata"

msgid ""
"Move real stock down the chain and fulfill farmer requests against actual "
