msgstr "Sogeza hifadhi halisi chini ya mnyororo na timiza maombi ya wakulima kulingana na salio halisi."

msgid "District & Regional Officers"
msgstr "Maafisa wa Wilaya na Mkoa"

msgid ""
"Reports scoped to your own territory, downloadable as PDF, with full audit "
